;&lt;span id="postorig_572356910"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ftc%2Flocal%2F682027e820c27a26afbd754e%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E8%258C%2582%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2594%25BE%25E7%25B7%25A9-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%258B%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585%25E6%2588%25B0&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=dc86e205147fb32678125aa63a61155c&amp;amp;fid=57" target="_blank"&gt;https://news.tvb.com/tc/local/68 ... -政府將繼續協助企業開拓市場應對關稅戰&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;陳茂波說：「我們是自由港、沒有外匯管制，所以我們歡迎資金來，都要做好準備隨時它走，所以金融穩定、金融安全我們很小心。對我們資產市場都有點幫助，但會否像過往般很快飆升，我覺得又不一定，畢竟供求情況不同了。另外要看回經濟，經濟雖然對我們而言相對比較穩，但都不是很熾熱情況。」&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他預期息口回落，股票市場會好轉，目前多間企業正輪候上市，對政府經營帳目有幫助，預測今個財政年度大致收支平衡，如資本市場持續興旺，甚至可能有盈餘。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31924523&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=141041294468207df33b2861_91111090"/><published>2025-05-11T18:36:50+08:00</published></entry></feed>